                    <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">2026 Regulatory Compliance Warning</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                        With the full enforcement of the Economic Crime and Corporate Transparency Act (ECCTA), Companies House has banned the use of simple P.O. Box addresses. Registered offices must be physical, appropriate locations where documents can be acknowledged by a person. Our service is 100% compliant with these active requirements.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

