                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I use this address for my personal bank accounts?</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">No. The registered office address is strictly for corporate correspondence and public listings with Companies House and HMRC. It should not be used as a personal bank billing address.</p>
